Package: testDoctor
Type: Package
Title: Generates markdown Documents of the test results using the testthat infrastructure
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ellis Hughes (auth,cre)
Maintainer: Ellis Hughes <ellishughes@live.com>
Description:
    This package takes advantage of the testthat infrastructure to generate more robust documentation surrounding the documentation of test passings and failings. The purpose of this is to provide a physical document indicating to the end user the results of each test in a clear manner and which version of the build that passed.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Require: 
    testthat,
    R6,
    devtools,
    here,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    tibble,
    withr
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
